[div class=p 
	"There are 4 types of stages in each map (M):
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Overhead map (魔境マップ)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Side-scroll makyo stage (4 大魔境)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Vertical-scroll hell stage (妖怪地獄)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Boss castle (妖怪城)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"There are 5 types of makyo gates:
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Grass field or house (妖界魔境)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Cemetery, shrine, riverbed or forest (妖奇魔境)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Death's head or warehouse (妖炎魔境)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Mountaion tops, treetops, icebergs or limestone cave (妖空魔境)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Makyo at random (ミステリー魔境)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"First you need to get a crystal ball (水晶玉) at one of the makyo to enter the boss castle. You can avoid the hell stage by selecting the correct door which appears at the end of makyo. Each boss has specific weak point, so you need to choose a proper special weapon in each makyo to beat it as quickly as possible.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"There are 4 special weapons:
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Finger pistols (指鉄砲) though it doesn't look like a finger
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Fireballs (火炎)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Chanchanko vests (ちゃんちゃんこ)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Remote-controlled geta shoes (リモコン下駄)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
